Close proximity to local neighborhood park with sports fields, pool, frisbee golf & pickle ball. Short travel distance to I-95 & Vero Beach. 15 minute drive to downtown Ft. Pierce area ,restaurants & beach areas. A/C -2022, roof 2007, newer garage door & opener. Rooms sizes approximate , and subject to error.
